Features: * Tiny performance improvements (Windows) * Improves the reliability of hostname retrieval (Title, Windows) Bugfixes: * Fixes potential compilation issues on Linux (#2142, Linux) * Fixes compilation errors on macOS when building with older SDKs (#2140, macOS) * Fixes compilation issues when building with `-DENABLE_SYSTEM_YYJSON=ON` (#2143) Logos: * Updates PrismLinux and adds a small variant ---
